(22786, 43808, 0, 1, 'The CON', 'Though the Lyrics to The Con are Militant Hippi inspired, this is one of those songs that just happened.\r\n\r\nA Warm up Jam, a perking of the ears, a smile and an exclamation, "this is a Radio Song!'' reverberating through the studio...  \r\n\r\nWait til you hear it Live! \r\n\r\nThe CON is Full of piss & vinegar and is music that will have you shaking your hips and raising your fist in the air.\r\n\r\nThis is a Live favorite...', '2010-02-12 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '(in Part - First Verse)\r\n\r\nWhy is the word CON in CONsider?\r\nThe Earth being sold to the Highest Bidder\r\nCONsider the CONstitution\r\nThe 1st Amerikan Revolution\r\nAnd now Evolution\r\nGive us Revolution Number 2\r\nOr World War III for me and you\r\nStand up\r\nGet Up\r\nI''m getting Fed Up\r\nHere''s the Heads up - so get your Meds up\r\nThe Powers that Be \r\nWon''t let us Be...', '', 306, '', 'Native Space', 'Boston Paul', 'Refuge Studio', 'Refuge Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-02-25 23:41:34', '2015-03-12 13:41:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
