(22788, 43808, 0, 1, 'Good Ol'' Dayzzz', 'Boston Paul wrote the lyrics to this song many years ago. \r\n\r\nThe Lyrics were used in a song called ''Theze R the Good Ol'' Dazed''  done by his other band Militant Hippi. When the BP''s fellow front man Justin went back to Canada, the song was put in the archives.\r\n\r\nNative Space has taken these lyrics that hold special meaning for BP and reworked the Music...  the rest as they say, is History.', '2008-03-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '(in part)\r\n\r\nI remember sitting on my grandaddy''s knee\r\nAnd every single day he be saying to me\r\nSon, my life was a flash and I don''t know when...\r\nI wish I could do it all over again...\r\nSo listen to me boy when I say to you\r\nLive everyday to yourself be true\r\nKeep courage in your heart and live without fear\r\nI remember staring into that log fire listening to my grandaddy say...\r\n\r\nThese are the Good Ol'' Days....', '', 250, '', 'Boston Paul & Native Space', 'Boston Paul', 'Refuge Studios', 'Refuge Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-02-26 00:08:40', '2015-03-12 13:41:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
